## TESTING

### Required Tests for Each Service
```
prayerService.js    → test API call, parsing, fallback on failure
contentService.js   → test rotation logic, index wrapping
countdownService.js → test next prayer calc, midnight edge case, all-prayers-passed case
aplBuilder.js       → test APL output has required fields
```

### Test Naming Convention
```javascript
describe('prayerService', () => {
  it('should return 5 prayer times for valid coordinates', async () => {});
  it('should return cached times when API fails', async () => {});
  it('should correctly identify next prayer after Asr', () => {});
});
```

### Test Files Location
```
lambda/__tests__/
  prayerService.test.js
  contentService.test.js
  countdownService.test.js
  aplBuilder.test.js
```

