## USEFUL COMMANDS

```bash
# Local testing
sam local invoke PrayerTimesFunction --event events/launch.json
sam local start-api

# Deploy
sam build && sam deploy

# Alexa Skill
ask deploy --target skill-metadata
ask deploy --target lambda
ask dialog --locale en-US

# Logs
sam logs -n PrayerTimesFunction --stack-name tawkit-echo --tail

# Run tests
npm test
npm run test:watch
```
